<subSubSection lastPageId="21" lastPageNumber="22" pageId="20" pageNumber="21" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="20.[151,1437,1374,1869]" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,253,1735,1761]" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">Key.</emphasis>
The digital, multiple-entry key “ 
<taxonomicName authorityName="de Meijere" authorityYear="1914" box="[623,884,1735,1761]" class="Insecta" family="Drosophilidae" genus="Colocasiomyia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="20" pageNumber="21" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cristata">
<emphasis box="[623,884,1735,1761]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">Colocasiomyia cristata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
species subgroup” to all species of this subgroup has been constructed largely based on the character matrix of Appendix 6, and is available from the following website: https://evolgen.biol.se.tmu.ac.jp/Classification/index.jsp (Biological Classification and Identification System).
</paragraph>
